Hardware Implementation
1.ESP8266 NodeMCU
2.DHT11 Temperature and Humidity Sensor
3.Breadboard
4.Jumper Wires
5.Micro USB Cable (for power and data)

Software Requirements
1.Arduino IDE 2.3.4
2.DHT sensor library (for reading temperature and humidity).
3.ESP8266WiFi library (for Wi-Fi communication).

References
https://arduino.esp8266.com/stable/package_esp8266com_index.json
